text: Strangely enough if all you want is sectional timings, I've just received an email in my inbox from proform (I'm a previous subscriber) about some deal with TPD (and others) to get the sectional timings as part of the profotm database. Seems like they are looking for an initial group of subs who are willing to pay for a year upfront (about £600). I realise this is totally different to a full GPS history, but thought I'd mention it anyway.

text: Just to be clear it is just SECTIONAL times - You'd need a platinum level sub and I'm not sure how much that is these days. If you are interested just email them and I'm sure they can send you the same email I received. Looks like they are looking for 50 initial people to cough up this 600 quid in order to make the deal. I didn't read in detail as I've no interest in it but send them an email and I;m sure you'll get the full story.
